        <updateDate>2020-07-09T22:22:02Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Buy America for Drinking Water Extension Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill makes permanent a requirement that projects financed through a drinking water state revolving fund program only use iron and steel products that are produced in the United States, unless the Environmental Protection Agency grants a waiver from the requirement. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
